<li>Sending you heartfelt condolences during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family as you mourn your furry friend.</li>
<li>Your pet brought so much joy to your lives.  May cherished memories bring you solace.</li>
<li>We were so saddened to hear about the passing of your dear pet.</li>
<li>May the love you shared bring comfort during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>Your pet will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>Holding you close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>I'm so sorry for your loss.</li>
<li>Sending love and strength your way.</li>
<li>May happy memories ease your pain.</li>
<li>Please accept our heartfelt condolences.</li>
<li>We will always remember your pet's loving spirit.</li>
<li>Your pet held a special place in all our hearts.</li>
<li>May your memories of your pet bring you peace.</li>
    

